items.desc: Dragon Ball Wiki es la enciclopedia en español dedicada a la famosa franquicia creada por Akira Toriyama. Este proyecto creado el 26 de junio de 2006 en Wikia (ahora FANDOM) recopila información relacionada con sus productos; como la exitosa serie de manga, su versión de anime como Dragon Ball Z, Kai, Super y GT, además de material relacionado como videojuegos.

items.name: Dr. Seuss Wiki
items.title: Dr. Seuss Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Dr. Seuss Wiki!
items.desc: This wiki is the official collaborative encyclopedia about the Dr. Seuss.

items.name: Dragon Quest Wiki
items.title: Dragon Quest Wiki
items.headline: Dragon Quest Wiki
items.desc: Dragon Quest Wiki is devoted to Dragon Quest, a series of role-playing games made by Square Enix (originally Enix Co.) for a variety of video game platforms. It is the all-time best-selling video game series in Japan. Every Dragon Quest game is told primarily through the eyes a Hero named by the player, usually a prophesied "Chosen One" or a similar concept that requires him to rise against a new evil.

items.name: DragonFable Wiki
items.title: DragonFable Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to DragonFable wiki
items.desc: DragonFable Wiki is a community dedicated to the Web-based Flash Role-Playing Game DragonFable, created and updated by Artix Entertainment, LLC. DFWiki aims to provide a comprehensive and accurate store of information about DragonFable that is mostly editable, with the exception of this main page to prevent vandalism. DragonFable requires nothing more than an Internet connection, a Web browser, and version 8.0 or above of the free plug-in Macromedia Flash to play.

items.name: American Dragon Jake Long
items.title: American Dragon Jake Long
items.headline: Welcome to the American Dragon: Jake Long Wiki!
items.desc:
American Dragon: Jake Long is an American superhero animated television series It marked the first animated Disney Channel Original Series. It produced by Walt Disney Television Animation created by Jeff Goode. It premiered on Disney Channel on January 21, 2005 and was discontinued on September 1, 2007.

Set in New York City (specifically the borough of Manhattan), this animated series tells the story of thirteen-year-old Jake Long who must balance ordinary adolescent transformation with the amazing power and ability to change into the form of a dragon. When he eventually unlocks his full potential and turns into the American Dragon, he will overcome obstacles to protect the magical creatures living in the city, but as his ordinary self, Jake Long can't conquer his huge romantic crush on the pretty blond schoolmate Rose who, unbeknownst to Jake, has a dark, magical secret of her own. She's a natural dragon slayer named Huntsgirl, a member of the Huntsclan that slay dragons. Jake navigates the city with fellow skateboarders Trixie Carter and Arthur P. Spuddinski (A.K.A Spud), and when he gets home, it's to an extended family: a businessman dad originally from the Midwest who doesn't know he's married into a family of dragons from his Chinese wife named Susan. Jake's maternal grandfather Laoshi (who recently immigrated to train his grandson in the magical, mystical ways of the ancient dragons), younger seven-year-old sister Haley (a nascent dragon), and Grandpa's gruff sidekick, a magical Shar-Pei named Fu Dog.

items.name: Nights into Dreams Wiki
items.title: Nights into Dreams Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Nights Wiki!
items.desc: NiGHTS into Dreams (or Nights into Dreams), is a video game released by Sega in 1996 for the Sega Saturn video game system. The game's story follows two children entering a dream world, where they are aided by a being called NiGHTS. This Wiki focuses on the the games and the characters of the NiGHTS universe, please contribute if you have something to add!

items.name: The New Systems Commonwealth Wiki
items.title: The New Systems Commonwealth Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Andromeda!
items.desc:
Andromeda was conceived by Gene Roddenberry in the early 1970s and posthumously produced on his behalf by his widow Majel Barrett-Roddenberry. Captain Dylan Hunt is a member of the Systems Commonwealth's High Guard; he and his ship the Andromeda Ascendant are frozen in time. They awaken 300 years in the future, where Hunt discovers that the Commonwealth has fallen and the universe has fallen into chaos, with the strong preying on the weak. Deciding to change all of this, Hunt sets out with a new crew to create a new Commonwealth and bring order to a chaotic galaxy. With this impossible task in front of him, Dylan must come up with a way to convince races to sign up while fighting off some of the galaxy's most fearsome enemies, including the Magog (and their god the Spirit of the Abyss) and the Nietzscheans, whilst also dealing with the problems and betrayals of the members of his new crew.

"The long night has come. The Systems Commonwealth the greatest civilization in history has fallen. Now, one ship, one crew have vowed to drive back the night and rekindle the light of civilization. On the starship Andromeda hope lives again"

— Intro to Season One

"He is the last guardian of a fallen civilization, a hero from another time. Faced with a universe in chaos, Dylan Hunt recruits an unlikely crew and sets out to reunite the galaxies. On the starship Andromeda hope lives again "
— Intro to Season Two

"The Universe is a dangerous place. But in our future my crew and I fight to make it safe. I am Dylan Hunt, Captain of the Andromeda Ascendant, and these are our adventures."
— Intro to Seasons Three, Four and Five

items.name: Drawn Together Wiki
items.title: Drawn Together Wiki
items.headline: Drawn Together Wikia
items.desc: Welcome to the Drawn Together Wikia! The Drawn Together Wikia is a comprehensive database about Drawn Together, an American animated television series on Comedy Central. The series is an animated sitcom set on a fictitious TV reality show that follows eight cartoon characters agreed to live in a house together in a setup similar to that of The Real World! Enter now to learn more about the series, characters, and more!

items.name: Drake and Josh Wiki
items.title: Drake and Josh Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Drake and Josh Wiki!
items.desc: Drake and Josh Wiki is collaborative fansite which provide fans with information on all aspects of the hit Nickelodeon television series, Drake & Josh. It aired on Nickelodeon from January 11, 2004 – September 16, 2007 for four seasons and a total of 60 episodes plus a TV Film. If you are a fan of Drake & Josh, please contribute to the wiki!

items.name: DRIV3R Wiki
items.title: DRIV3R Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Driv3r wiki!
items.desc: This wiki is about the PC, PS2, Xbox and Game Boy Advance game, Driv3r, originally known as Driver 3, which is also the 3rd installment of the Driver series. It features all the characters, vehicles, weapons, businesses, cities, glitches, secrets, etc in the game! Don't be afraid to stop by and get a good guide on this game, even though it's pretty old now. We can help you out!

items.name: Dr Slump Wiki
items.title: Dr Slump Wiki
items.headline: Visit Dr. Slump Wiki
items.desc: Dr. Slump Wiki is a collaborative database on the Dr. Slump manga by Akira Toriyama and the anime series created by Toei Animation. The series follows the scientist Senbei Norimaki and the android girl Arale living among the strange residents of Penguin Village. We have information on the characters, universe, manga chapters, anime episodes, films, video games and many other content related to the series.

items.name: Uncharted Wiki
items.title: Uncharted Wiki
items.headline: Uncharted Wiki
items.desc: Uncharted Wiki contains nearly 1500 pages on the Uncharted series and maintains their own Twitter account. Uncharted is a series of video games developed by the award-winning company Naughty Dog for the PlayStation 3. Each game revolves around the adventures of protagonist Nathan Drake; a modern-day treasure hunter and action pro, as he attempts to unearth various historical mysteries.

items.name: Dreamworks Animation Wiki
items.title: Dreamworks Animation Wiki
items.headline: DreamWorks Wiki
items.desc:
DreamWorks Wiki is a collaborative encyclopedia for everything related to DreamWorks and its work. Here at this wiki, you can find, create, and edit articles on DreamWorks and its subsidiaries: Theme parks, movie companies, television networks, movies, characters, and more!
The wiki format allows anyone with a username to create or edit any article so we can all work together to create a comprehensive database for DreamWorks fans!

items.name: Driver enciclopedia
items.title: Driver enciclopedia
items.headline: Bienvenido a Driver Enciclopedia
items.desc:
Driver Enciclopedia, es un proyecto creado el día 29 de Agosto 2010 donde todo el mundo puede editar sobre la saga de videojuegos, Driver.

La Saga Driver es una serie de videojuegos desarrollado por la empresa Reflections Interactive, que se habían encontrado anteriormente con Destruction Derby en los primeros años de la PlayStation.
La saga Driver empezó en 1998 con su primer videojuego, Driver desarrollado por Reflections. El género de esta saga es conducción/acción y sandbox que es bastante parecida a su saga rival, Grand Theft Auto.

items.name: Dead Rising Wiki
items.title: Dead Rising Wiki
items.headline: Dead Rising Wiki
items.desc: Dead Rising Wiki is a site that covers everything related to Dead Rising. Information is provided about characters, locations, weapons, maps, screenshots, videos, walkthroughs, guides, zombies, and more.

items.name: Blue Dragon Wiki
items.title: Blue Dragon Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Blue Dragon Wikia
items.desc: The Blue Dragon Wikia is a community site dedicated to the Blue Dragon video game and its manga/anime adaptions. If you are a fan of Blue Dragon, or even if you're just curious about it, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and help us expand this database... or join us in discussion about the manga, the anime, or the game in general. All are welcome!

items.name: Dresden Files
items.title: Dresden Files
items.headline: Welcome to Dresden Files Wiki!
items.desc: The Dresden Files is a series of contemporary fantasy/mystery novels written by Jim Butcher. He provides a first person narrative of each story from the point of view of the main character, private investigator and wizard Harry Dresden, as he recounts investigations into supernatural disturbances in modern-day Chicago. Butcher's original proposed title for the first novel was Semiautomagic, which sums up the series' balance of fantasy and hard-boiled detective fiction.

items.name: The Legend of Dragoon Wiki
items.title: The Legend of Dragoon Wiki
items.headline: Help build the Legend of Dragoon Wiki
items.desc: The Legend of Dragoon Wiki hold tons of information on the PS1 cult hit The Legend of Dragoon! We want to get more help from other LOD fans and create a large encompassing knowledge of the great game. Released to America in 2000, The Legend of Dragoon is a turn-based JRPG that follows the story of Dart and his friends as they unravel a plot by the platinum-haired Lloyd and Emperor Diaz. This epic journey that spans 4 discs uses a new and original battle system called "additions" and gives the player the ability to turn their team into mystical dragon knights called "dragoons". Whether you are a old fan or a new fan or are new to the game entirely, join us and help build our community and add on to our pages!

items.name: Children's Books Wiki
items.title: Children's Books Wiki
items.headline: Children's Books Wiki
items.desc: Children's Books Wiki is a freely editable database about books written for children ages 0-16, and the young at heart. Each book has a description, readers' reviews, guidance on content, recommended reading age and suggestions for what to read next. Come and visit the only collaborative website dedicated to children's books!

items.name: Dragonball Fanon Wiki
items.title: Dragonball Fanon Wiki
items.headline: Dragon Ball Fanon Wiki
items.desc: Dragon Ball is one of the most popular mangas/animes of all time. With three story arcs, it has amassed a huge following of fans, many of whom enjoy the meta-series so much they create their own additions to Dragon Ball tale. These additions are known as fan fictions, or "fanons". Started in 2008, Dragon Ball Fanon Wiki is designed so that anyone can edit and add their own Dragon Ball, Dragon Ball Z, and/or Dragon Ball GT fan fiction and read other people's fan fictions. We accept almost all kinds of fan fiction, no matter what the content is, so long as it is inoffensive and appropriate for all ages.

items.name: Die drei Fragezeichen Wiki
items.title: Die drei Fragezeichen Wiki
items.headline: Das Wiki zur Kultserie "Die drei Fragezeichen"
items.desc:
Hier findest du alles rund um die erfolgreiche Buch- und Hörspielserie: Infos über die drei Detektive, ihre Fälle, ihre Freunde und Freundinnen, Feinde und Feindinnen, und und und...

Doch all das entsteht nicht von alleine: Das Die Drei ??? Wiki kann die Hilfe von Jedem und Jeder gebrauchen, um es mit Wissen zu füllen! Es ist ganz einfach!

items.name: Dragonica Wiki
items.title: Dragonica Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Dragonica Wikia!
items.desc: Dragonica, or Dragonica Online is a 3D/2D, fantasy, action-oriented, side scrolling Massive Multiplayer Online Role-Playing Game (or MMORPG) developed by Barunson Interactive. The European version is published by Gpotato, the Korean version by PlayNC, Chinese version by Playcool, the US Version by THQ*ICE, and the SEA-ANZ version by IAHGames. It is a F2P game with a cash shop. It plays similar to other "action-arcade" games such as Lunia.  It is comparable to the 2-dimensional MMORPGs, LaTale and MapleStory.

items.name: Total Drama Wiki
items.title: Total Drama Wiki
items.headline: Live the action on the Total Drama Wiki
items.desc: Founded on July 6, 2008, the Total Drama Wiki is a collaborative wiki focusing on Total Drama, a franchise that lampoon the conventions commonly found in reality shows. It premiered on the Canadian television channel Teletoon, on July 8, 2007 and the American television channel Cartoon Network, on June 5, 2008. Make sure to check our wiki for all the details on Total Drama.

items.name: Drawn to Life Wiki

items.headline: The Drawn to Life Wikia
items.desc: Welcome to the Drawn to Life Wikia! This is the wikia about Drawn to Life that anyone can edit! Drawn to Life is an action-adventure game for the Nintendo DS where players can create their own playable characters, levels, objects, and accessories by drawing them using the DS's stylus & touch screen.The premise of the game is to free a cursed village from surrounding darkness! Enter the wikia now to learn more!

items.desc: Dr. Gregory House, gespielt von Hugh Laurie, ist der Protagonist der TV-Serie Dr. House. Dr. House ist ein Einzelgänger und ein Genie auf dem Gebiet der Medizin. Er leitet die diagnostische Abteilung im fiktiven Princeton-Plainsboro Teaching Hospital.

items.name: Married with Children Wiki
items.title: Married with Children Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Married With Children Wiki
items.desc:
Married... with Children ran for eleven seasons, totaling 262 episodes and airing from April 5, 1987 to June 9, 1997. The series was also renown for it's handling of topic and subject matter that were at the time, considered non-standard which earned it both praise and criticism.

The show followed the lives of Al Bundy (Ed O'Neill), a once-glorious high school football player turned hard-luck salesman of women's shoes, and his family.

Feel free to contact any of the admins if you have further questions and enjoy your time on the wiki!

This place is full of creative original characters, fan work and pictures, and you can join too! Create your own stories, art or other content, based on any of the Nickelodeon series or characters.

items.name: Android Wiki
items.title: Android Wiki
items.desc: The Android Wiki is a collaborative, public, and free encyclopedia about anything related to the Android operating system. From Material Design, to the Linux kernel, to the Google Pixel, to the Android Open Source Project, anything Android can be found here.

items.name: Dragon ball AF Wiki
items.title: Dragon ball AF Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Dragonball AF Wikia
items.desc: Dragon Ball AF (ドラゴンボールAF, Doragon Bōru AF) was the subject of an "April Fool's" joke in 1997 (following the end of Dragon Ball GT, the third and last series), which concerned a fourth anime installment of the Dragon Ball series. It has since gained popularity, been the basis for various fictional works by fans, and has even resulted in a dōjinshi series produced by Toyble.

items.name: Dr House Wiki
items.title: Dr House Wiki
items.headline: Housepedia
items.desc: Housepedia es la enciclopedia en español dedicada a la exitosa serie de televisión House M. D. Este proyecto recopila toda la información referente al trabajo del Dr. Gregory House al frente del equipo de diagnóstico en un hospital de Nueva Jersey; tratando aspectos como los personajes, actores o episodios.

items.name: Dream Theater Wiki
items.title: Dream Theater Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Dream Theater Wikia!
items.desc:
This wikia is dedicated to Dream Theater, which is a Progressive Metal band from Long Island, New York formed originally as "Majesty" by their three core members Mike Portnoy, John Petrucci and John Myung, who have remained with the band since it's inception in 1985. Other current members include James LaBrie and Jordan Rudess, and former members include Kevin Moore, Chris Collins, Charlie Dominici, Steve Stone and Derek Sherinian.

Help us edit our wikia!

items.name: Wiki Dragon Age
items.title: Wiki Dragon Age
items.headline: Bienvenue sur Wiki Dragon Age
items.desc:
Dragon Age est une série de jeux vidéo de type RPG (jeu de rôle) créée par la société canadienne Bioware (Baldur's Gate, Neverwinter Nights, Mass Effect).

Les deux premiers jeux, Dragon Age: Origins et Dragon Age II, ont été agrémentés par beaucoup de contenu téléchargeable.

L'univers fantastique de la série est également utilisé dans une variété d'autres médias, comprenant les livres et les jeux de société.

Puedes ver todo sobre las seis temporadas: Isla del Drama, Luz Drama Acción, Drama Total: Gira Mundial, Drama Total la Venganza de la Isla, Total Drama All-Stars ¡e incluso sobre la 6ª temporada: Total Drama: Pahkitew Island! ¡No seas tímido y empieza a vivir el drama!

items.name: Drachen Wiki
items.title: Drachen Wiki
items.headline: Willkommen im Drachen Wiki
items.desc: Dieses Wiki ist eine Enzyklopädie über Drachen aller Art, zu der alle Fans von Mythologie und Fantasy beitragen können. Obwohl ähnliche Kreaturen in der Mythologie mit Tiamat und Mušḫuššu schon seit mehreren tausend Jahren bekannt sind und bereits 700 n.Chr. durch Beowulf annähernd ihre heutige Form annahmen, tut dies ihrer Beliebtheit keinen Abbruch. Während man in Spielen noch traditionell gegen Monster wie Alduin den Weltenfresser oder Rathalos kämpft (und dabei die eine oder andere Prinzessin rettet), erfreuen sich komplexe Charaktere wie Smaug oder Ohnezahn in Filmen immer größerer Beliebtheit.  Wer sich für eine wissenschaftliche Interpretation dieser Wesen interessiert, sollte sich unsere Artikel zur Drakologie ansehen, z.B. über die Entstehung des Feuers oder die Erklärung der Flugfähigkeit.  Das Wiki freut sich über die Mitarbeit von jedem, der sich für Lindwürmer interessiert. Wenn dabei noch Unklarheiten bestehen, könnt ihr euch jederzeit an EbrithilBowser wenden.

items.name: Dragonica Wiki
items.title: Dragonica Wiki
items.headline: Dragonica Wiki MMORPG
items.desc:
Dragonica est un MMORPG d'aventure-action en 3D à l'ambiance manga décalée et originale. Choisissez entre 6 classes, le guerrier, le magicien, l'archer, le voleur; le chaman et l'amazone.
Et explorez les merveilles et les dangers de terres lointaines ! Combattez des dragons, des gargouilles et des monstres avec vos amis pour rétablir la paix sur le monde de Dragotaka.
Le plus génial c'est que le jeu Dragonica est gratuit !

items.name: Wiki Dragon Ball

items.name: Dragon Ball Wiki
items.title: Dragon Ball Wiki
items.headline: ドラゴンボール ウィキアへようこそ！誰でも編集できるファンコミュニティに参加してみよう！
items.desc: ドラゴンボールシリーズの漫画、アニメ、登場人物、用語など様々な情報で溢れるファンコミュニティです！ドラゴンボールに関する情報や感想をファン同士で共有する場です。ドラゴンボールに関しての疑問は、このコミュニティで見つかります！ドラゴンボール、ドラゴンボールZ、ドラゴンボールGT、ドラゴンボール改に関する画像や動画、詳しい情報が満載です。まずはお気に入りのキャラクターから検索してみましょう！ このコミュニティでは、ドラゴンボールについて知っていることを誰でも追加していただけます。ファン同士で情報共有しながら、フォーラムで感想を語り合い、コミュニティの仲間を増やしながらドラゴンボールシリーズに関する知識を一緒に深め合いましょう！
